title: Other Historic Areas, Washington DC, 2006
name: Other Historic Areas, Washington DC, 2006
description: This is a consolidated collection of areas with historical significance within the District of Columbia as listed in the "District of Columbia Inventory of Historic Sights, 2004". It contains the locations and attributes of parks, cemetaries, archaeological sites, fort circle parks, highways, canals, and other areas of historical worth which do not have National Historic Park or National Historic Site status. Note that not all features in this data set are currently officially designated as historic, and not all structures that may be eligible for historic designation are included. Additional datasets are available that include (1) Historic Districts, National Historic Parks and National Historic Sites, and (2) Historic Structures. The same records in this polygon-format dataset are also available in a point-format dataset.
